Step-by-Step Structure to Build
AI Smart Complaint Management System

1) Step 1 - Project Planning

First decide what your system will do.

Users
- Citizen / Student / Customer (submit complaint)
- Admin (manage complaints)

Core Features
- User login & signup
- Submit complaint
- AI automatically categorizes complaint
- Admin dashboard
- Complaint status tracking
- Analytics charts

2) Step 2 - Choose Technology Stack

Frontend
- React.js
- Tailwind CSS
- Chart.js

Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

Database
- MongoDB

AI Module
- Python
- Scikit-learn
- NLP (TF-IDF)

